data.name: lbl_DragDropStuck.Text
data.value: It seems like the drag && drop panel is stuck... - No worries, this happens when you are moving the cursor too fast and the UI doesn't have time to update. Yeah... #WinForms I detected that and I got you covered. Just move the cursor outside of the panel (or on this text). That's it! :)

data.name: cmb_OpenReportWith.ToolTip
data.value: ALEx automatically searches in your system for the following text editors: VS Code, Sublime Text, Notepad++, Atom and Notepad. If no text editor is found, an option to copy the report to the clipboard will be shown.

data.name: chk_OpenReport.ToolTip
data.value:
After the processing finishes, the report will be automatically opened in the selected text editor.
Note: the files paths in the report are using / (forward slash) instead of \ (backslash), because in JSON you have to escape \ and therefore it would appear as \\ (double backslashes). By using / you can copy and paste the path in Windows Explorer and it will still work. ;)

data.name: chk_CopyReportToCB.ToolTip
data.value:
After the processing finishes, the report will be automatically copied to the clipboard.
Note: the files paths in the report are using / (forward slash) instead of \ (backslash), because in JSON you have to escape \ and therefore it would appear as \\ (double backslashes). By using / you can copy and paste the path in Windows Explorer and it will still work. ;)
